$$
\begin{gathered}
A_{100}=2^{98}+A_{98} \\
A_{98}=2^{96}+A_{96} \\
\ldots \\
A_{6}=2^{4}+A_{4} \\
A_{4}=2^{2}+A_{2}
\end{gathered}
$$

